reviewText: Information was somewhat limited, like watching a commercial, they just touched on the highlights of woodland scenics products and their use. Im disappointed. I give three stars.
Great product just like all of the Woodland Scenics stuff. I advised everyone on Planet Earth to buy it ASAP.

I had hoped that this video would teach me how to use Woodland Scenics superb product line to make some awesome scenery for my model railroad. Instead, all I got was a very long commercial that I paid for.

This was not a total loss. The video went over all of their major products and demonstrated how they could be used but it was very light on giving actual techniques. It was just an advertisement. That being said, it did show off many of their products to good advantage and make me more likely to use their product line.
